# Desmos-SeedsCrawler
Simple script to grab seeds for desmos blockchain

# Usage
`git clone https://github.com/mgaldi/Desmos-SeedsCrawler.git && cd Desmos-SeedsCrawler` \
`chmod +x grab_seeds.sh` \
`./grab_seeds.sh <url/net_info?>`

# Example
`./grab_seeds.sh http://seed-4.morpheus.desmos.network:26657/net_info?`
